    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "6c3413b9-5354-4f7d-963a-f76602c652f1",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Botanists&apos; Pilfered Innovations",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ANCESTRAL_SMOOTHSNAKE",
        "PublicId": "133736656407",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_smoothsnake.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository a7f475df-23f6-4f4c-9907-3655d74d60c6).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon 47. Your targets  are world-famous botanists. They are known for creating the world&apos;s first bioengineered hybrid flowers, or so it seems. Our client was the original creator of the hybrid flower, however these three stole our client&apos;s invention and had risen in fame. We have located them in the Dartmoor Garden Show, as VIP guests in the event. Your client also wants you to steal a speedboat which belongs to one of the targets, containing biological data to the flower.\r\rGood luck.",
